{"tid":314261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遼寧號訪港】上艦睇美軍機？中年漢憶國恥想國家強大：最想睇F15","createTime":"2017-07-09T04:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T05:21:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2057b6a92323d71364cd132d435afda416c9123f","tid":314261,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170709/large/1499568178_7459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170709%2Flarge%2F1499568178_7459.jpg&h=92ebc6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 中國第一艘航空母艦「遼寧號」今日最後一日開放給獲派參觀券的公眾登艦，今早8時陸續有市民到場。<br />\n<br />\n不少市民今次其中一個目的是近距離觀看中國的殲15戰機，從事交通運輸的陳先生表示，相信未來兩年的航空母艦技術會超越遼寧號，「所以先開放畀我哋睇，如果唔係軍事科技唔會開放」，但他錯誤將殲15戰機說成「F15戰機(美軍)」，「(今次)最主要睇下F15戰機&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生又指，遼寧號於7月7日抵港，聯想到蘆溝橋事變，讓他想起中國的屈辱，希望透過遼寧號讓新一代了解，「中國依家局勢比以前好咗好多，但仍然危機四伏，當一個國家積弱，國民咩都唔係，所以最重要係國家強大」。<br />\n<br />\n任職金融行業的陳先生則覺得遼寧號是「國家軍事實力強大嘅一個表現，遼寧號可以嚟到香港畀我哋市民參觀，覺得係對香港一個關愛」；又指「作為一個市民會有興趣睇一睇，同埋係一種榮幸」。<br />\n<br />\n從事醫院工作的溫先生表示，主要是上遼寧號拍照，又指最期望看到殲15戰機。他說：「其實我本身鍾意睇相同乜都睇下嘅！」適逢有此機會和時間，所以早前排隊索取門票參觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170709/56932539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170709%2F56932539&d=Cv9dvMquDalcFwiy0o%2FDRL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=da979dbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170709%2F56932539&h=494b6a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170709/56932539</a>"},{"pid":"abaef4306fb0811a3d20deeaed1a69dec7acd5e3","tid":314261,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"J15"},{"pid":"a5a02094adbf3937d16abdf407fa8144800239d6","tid":314261,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302b4435f524c2e3dbd936b7023a26181f4874cd","tid":314261,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"殲15係咪抄返黎？"},{"pid":"0164d287982d737f6a8909caee0a12ffbe0bfb0a","tid":314261,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殲15係咪抄返黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抄外觀?"},{"pid":"4633d78513487e2f0c7ad1d1df861ce142186c2a","tid":314261,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢中"},{"pid":"41cda0fc575030f294edf21fca1d7d7302bad04d","tid":314261,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"艦載F15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db89e27d461a66c309c943f9fa0df65f95aad7f8","tid":314261,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"我都想係香港睇F15<br />\n最好長註<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1582e8a4054856b3aeb9bf05461abce867523e","tid":314261,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"國家愈強太<br />\n國民愈慘on99"},{"pid":"91500b8a7c022afaa4cd6098cb867eab733ab013","tid":314261,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>殲15係咪抄返黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抄外觀?</blockquote><br />\nSu-33 強國航艦版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7756528655cdb95ac47f7e1dced421d9a012824e","tid":314261,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/125759_80ec8cc1c1a56077a43c39ea1499d14d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F125759_80ec8cc1c1a56077a43c39ea1499d14d.jpg&h=99c4b33f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dc4227df2acc18bbec6749de9b9e390b0c573af","tid":314261,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>殲15係咪抄返黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抄外觀?</blockquote><br />\nSu-33 強國航艦版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n定得MIG-29級數？"},{"pid":"939bcd5d996a15f1e835a790ca4395783932448c","tid":314261,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>艦載F15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年F14啱啱服役奶緊野果時麥道真係向美國海軍sell過艦載F15依個concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bcbf4768b0b9b02ca5a98b40815cc71d2e68ec","tid":314261,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"睇SR71?"},{"pid":"8d96564f01db9213223a94d84d09d48547e24b1d","tid":314261,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>艦載F15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年F14啱啱服役奶緊野果時麥道真係向美國海軍sell過艦載F15依個concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n80年代曾經有過 F-16N，只係作為「假想敵用機」，但唔可以於航艦升降。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df0be5cbf99d137e6f0b91c2c95cb22d5146335","tid":314261,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}